<subSubSection id="C36B652A8136FF9AFF31FC4EFEF1FB7A" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BCE36A18136FF9AFF31FC4EFCBDFBCB" blockId="25.[136,1452,878,1192]" box="[189,782,1022,1049]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis id="B905EAB38136FF9AFF31FC4EFEC6FBCA" bold="true" box="[189,373,1022,1048]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Distribution:—</emphasis>
? 
<collectingCountry id="F36676318136FF9AFEF3FC4EFE43FBCA" box="[383,496,1022,1048]" name="Myanmar" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F36676318136FF9AFE77FC4EFDF2FBCA" box="[507,577,1022,1048]" name="China" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">China</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F36676318136FF9AFDC0FC4FFD3FFBCB" box="[588,652,1023,1049]" name="Japan" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Japan</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F36676318136FF9AFD4EFC4FFCB9FBCB" box="[706,778,1023,1049]" name="South Korea" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Korea</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCE36A18136FF9AFF31FB92FEF1FB7A" blockId="25.[136,1452,878,1192]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis id="B905EAB38136FF9AFF31FB92FEA8FBEE" bold="true" box="[189,283,1058,1084]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Note:—</emphasis>
The identity of the above-cited specimens is not certain. This and 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D228136FF9AFC7CFB93FB35FBEE" box="[1008,1158,1058,1084]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bletia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="formosana">
<emphasis id="B905EAB38136FF9AFC7CFB93FB35FBEE" box="[1008,1158,1058,1084]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">B. formosana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differ mainly in the extent of undulation of lip keels, and a detailed baseline comparison in this group is much needed. Also the newly described 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D228136FF9AFF04FBDAFD37FB56" authority="Jie Huang &amp; G. Z. Chen" authorityName="Jie Huang &amp; G. Z. Chen" box="[136,644,1130,1157]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bletilla" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="guizhouensis">
<emphasis id="B905EAB38136FF9AFF04FBDAFEC7FB56" box="[136,372,1130,1156]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Bletilla guizhouensis</emphasis>
Jie Huang &amp; G.Z.Chen
</taxonomicName>
from southern 
<collectingCountry id="F36676318136FF9AFCB8FBDAFCC4FB56" box="[820,887,1130,1156]" name="China" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">China</collectingCountry>
is superficially similar and should be included in this comparison.
</paragraph>
